{"tid":1354554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［727] 不要說「燒村」「拆祠堂」「光復」試著說「反恐」「守護」「抗暴」","createTime":"2019-07-23T07:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T19:36:00.000Z","uid":218570,"like":111,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"d96f8757d749af6bf2656c75507f41a97e2585ef","tid":1354554,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:10:33.000Z","msg":"首先利申 樓主住過元朗<br />\n<br />\n我同大家一樣 721睇直播嬲到仆街嘅<br />\n但最近太多講燒村 拆祠堂 以血還血嘅說話<br />\n其實咁會激起起元朗人嘅恐慌 驚大家會開大片<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住 要做嘅野 <br />\n唔需要咁大聲講出口</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要用文宣令大家清楚知道 <br />\n我地入元朗係要證明 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n我地唔怕佢地</span></span></span> <br />\n要保護市民 堅拒白色恐怖同恐怖襲擊！<br />\n<br />\n而唔係入去暴力復仇 當然 自衛一定要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要Connect埋元朗被欺壓 被滅聲嘅一群<br />\n仲有呢幾日被白色恐怖籠罩嘅所有和理非<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要50萬人入元朗 <br />\n50萬人一齊走！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n下面有兩篇好文 我地要將鄉黑同中央連埋一齊<br />\n同埋一定要打贏鄉黑！無論係精神上定肉體上<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【好緊要！幫推上頂！】美國同阿侵提哂水啦！　香港人下一步係要咁做呀！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354056</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[長文 歡迎討論] 其實有冇諗過贏左鄉黑就贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1352742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1352742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"35bd91a9cfa1d9e3f84f282eb5926dbae29d76ba","tid":1354554,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:11:08.000Z","msg":"守護元朗大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f4344ff373ccd53cfd8c1fb3d6df7c7d3b7a07","tid":1354554,"uid":218570,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:11:26.000Z","msg":"元朗反恐抗暴大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3228941ed6e841d497958c484219be32d597f866","tid":1354554,"uid":218570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:12:02.000Z","msg":"要聯合一切可以聯合嘅力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69084bfdfe9a720bebae3d3a7f22536a5db4011a","tid":1354554,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:12:48.000Z","msg":"記住 要光復嘅係香港 <br />\n要守護嘅係元朗被打壓嘅所有人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431fb4c4f7537a221d3202d8fd78188ffddd7af3","tid":1354554,"uid":281418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"反恐 push"},{"pid":"7d6cdb8a47e1731939d97c7548beb03a347a809c","tid":1354554,"uid":223233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:13:38.000Z","msg":"守護元朗大遊行！"},{"pid":"9cefc56548eb2230c159287df0b144d022a4619d","tid":1354554,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"守護元朗！！<br />\n香港人自保！！<br />\n極力對抗恐怖主義！！"},{"pid":"016013d6c44db72226d84bab4a57c80c6c2cf1e5","tid":1354554,"uid":218570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:14:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈譴責中央政府指示元朗黑社會勢力<br />\n作出國家級恐怖襲擊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f35edab6b4d2b722610175c103386dd6caaa8d","tid":1354554,"uid":53321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:14:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bbc554fbf71fcacc6493501b0f0f1e4927eb0637","tid":1354554,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:15:16.000Z","msg":"我地係反恐精英 打CS嘅夢想成真喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660bc2eaa0886dc0eb9e4139785d5bbcd3ef04f3","tid":1354554,"uid":48544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:15:17.000Z","msg":"[727光復元朗]  727元朗反黑反恐行動部署提議<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354479</a><br />\n<br />\n可以睇下我嘅提議～<br />\n<br />\n727光復元朗 (副題：元朗反黑反恐行動) <br />\n口號：肅清鄉黑，除暴安良 <br />\n目的：以武力震懾元朗鄉黑勢力，保障元朗社區安全。 <br />\n<br />\n727香港人嘅主要目標有 <br />\n1. 針對鄉黑黃賭毒勢力經濟進行破壞 (首要目標：黃色經濟) <br />\n<br />\n大家唔好唔記得除咗元朗有黑社會之外。 <br />\n元朗區同屯門公園一樣，有色情流鶯問題。 <br />\n掃鄉黑圍村個時，幫埋元朗區搞掂埋黃色問題。 <br />\n<br />\n建議： <br />\n進行141洗樓行動，對流鶯進行驅趕。 <br />\n為咗cut班鄉黑嘅收入 <br />\n<br />\n一樓一地址141個網有架啦。我睇下post唔post出嚟 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非都可以係一樓一門口貼下紙仔 <br />\n個人推介可以貼五十路林鄭av封面圖同鄭若驊大波圖係一樓一舊樓門口。 <br />\n<br />\n勇武手足可以注意睇下啲粉紅光管，啲門口cam可以點做。<br />\n<br />\n同埋call埋入境處舉報有人違反逗留條件，入境處都有執法嘅權力。 <br />\n<br />\n舉報違反入境條例罪行 <a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/immigration/investigation/onlinereportoffence.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Fimmigration%2Finvestigation%2Fonlinereportoffence.htm&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=7ff6cee5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/immigration/investigation/onlinereportoffence.htm</a><br />\n電話：入境事務處24小時舉報熱線： (852) 2824 1551 (舉報後獲提供一個檔案編號) <br />\n<br />\n人地已經ready <br />\n［遍地開花］年輕紀律部隊要爬山 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1354244/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1354244/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n麻雀館大家睇下可以點搞，我唔熟"},{"pid":"9f477fbc51343d5a695ab81222684fa33b3c84d0","tid":1354554,"uid":217844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:15:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f71c5e4fac766b0c2bad88cef8a94d8fa8fc8a5b","tid":1354554,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbc554fbf71fcacc6493501b0f0f1e4927eb0637","tid":1354554,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:15:16.000Z","msg":"我地係反恐精英 打CS嘅夢想成真喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:15:30.000Z","msg":"counter-strike<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2235724bfe607fb0e9df664d62d74298573fe8","tid":1354554,"uid":272010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:15:39.000Z","msg":"無錯,大家都好憤怒,不過我地係正義之師,遣詞用字方面就要同班恐怖分子劃清界線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08a0063ee87415f9e2e4f2bfb4a3b40c7771bd3","tid":1354554,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:16:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f16dafd979223162c7315158aef28aa3b0bdb606","tid":1354554,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa2235724bfe607fb0e9df664d62d74298573fe8","tid":1354554,"uid":272010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:15:39.000Z","msg":"無錯,大家都好憤怒,不過我地係正義之師,遣詞用字方面就要同班恐怖分子劃清界線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:16:34.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"56efe96728f933a82588d14ede3a489d155be5af","tid":1354554,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:16:53.000Z","msg":"此